<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm von Wolfstein zu Sulzbürg</head><p>Der Rat bittet Wilhelm um Bezahlung seiner schon lange ausstehenden Schulden bei Fritz Kammermeister, Bürger zu Nürnberg,</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_343" id="171r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_343_r1l2">VVılhelm von wolffſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l3">cʒu der Solcʒpürg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_343_r1l4"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vvılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> / Vns hat furgelegt fricʒ <expan>Camermeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie Jr Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l5">etwieuil ſchuldig beleibt / des er ewr brief hab vnd das Jm etwıelang </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l6">awſſengeſtanden ſeẏ vnd nicht beʒalt kunn <expan>vverd<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd maint auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l8">Er vvolt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_343_r1l7">ew </ab></add> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> furgewendt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das vvir Jn von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l9">cʒu dercʒeit dauon geweiſet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein ſchulde noch rıchten vnd <expan>beʒale<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Jn auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l11"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> vnklaghafft <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvöllet Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Antwurt </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_343_r1l13"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Mıch<ex>aelis</ex></expan> <expan>A<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> xj<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_343" id="171r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm von Wolffstein czu der Solczpürg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>, uns hat furgelegt Fricz
                                <expan>Camermeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie ir im etwievil schuldig beleibt, des er
                        ewr brief hab und das im etwielang awssengestanden sey und nicht bezalt kunn
                                <expan>werd<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und maint auch, er wolt
                            <add>ew</add>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> furgewendt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das wir in von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czu der czeit davon geweiset
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein schulde noch richten und
                                <expan>bezale<ex>n</ex></expan> und in auch
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> unklaghafft
                            <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Mich<ex>aelis</ex></expan>
<expan>a<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> xj<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
